cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about improving convolutional neural networks for mobile applications, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes novel operations and architectural units, which could be considered as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) research. Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on image classification tasks, which could be categorized as multimedia (cs.MM) research.
